<p itemprop="description">Leadership involves inspiring, guiding and influencing others to achieve shared goals, creating vision and direction, building high-performing teams, and driving positive change in organisations.</p>

<div class="proficiency-levels">
    <h2>Proficiency Levels</h2>

    <ol class="skill-levels">
        <li>
            <h3>Awareness</h3>
            <p>You can understand different leadership styles and recognise effective leadership behaviours. You can take responsibility for your own work and support team objectives.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <h3>Working</h3>
            <p>You can lead small teams or projects, motivate others, delegate effectively, and take responsibility for team outcomes. You can adapt your leadership style to different situations.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <h3>Practitioner</h3>
            <p>You can lead complex teams and initiatives, create compelling vision and strategy, develop others, drive organisational change, and influence across boundaries.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <h3>Expert</h3>
            <p>You can provide executive leadership, shape organisational culture and values, lead transformation at scale, influence at senior levels, and develop leadership capability across the organisation.</p>
        </li>
    </ol>
</div>

